I completely diagree with this notion.  First it is not about revenge it's about justice.  As for violent inclinations, this a baby we are talking about.  What the fuck does any baby do to deserve such treatment?  People become outraged when bad shit is done to little kids, even moreso when it's a baby and I for one hope that never changes.<br>
